{"tid":182811,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣（113）這個借給你用   這是我考試用的勝負筆   所以加油哦","createTime":"2017-04-01T15:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T05:20:46.000Z","uid":25382,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d620f5be77956c3b069cb925d9d30b12dfe2111","tid":182811,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">DSE嘅巴打加油</div></span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><blockquote>▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼<br />\n- 全舊post連結：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/GEzE2n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FGEzE2n&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=e96f63f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/GEzE2n</a><br />\n- 近期消息整合：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/O3I76l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FO3I76l&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=54636325\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/O3I76l</a><br />\n-新post格式：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/1RJM5F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F1RJM5F&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=70532d66\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/1RJM5F</a><br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2樓入門攻略、投票區、綜藝<br />\n廣告、相集、Google drive綜合下載</strong></span><br />\n- 3樓新劇/電影資訊<br />\n長都一定要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爬晒先好黎問野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>溫馨提示</strong></span></span><br />\n- 內文經常自動轉台離題 歡迎參與討論<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">如果有人搞事可以自動波扑佢</span><br />\n-有咩相關新資源可以擺上黎<br />\n-頭post出齊先好留名 記得正皮<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/20/221937_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F20%2F221937_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=33a27c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>標題來源：</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pRheex9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpRheex9.gif&h=90a5363e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>3月23&amp;24日新SP<br />\n《羈絆～奔跑吧！奇蹟的小馬～》</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVhD1G8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVhD1G8.jpg&h=849e0da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ts00fs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ts00fs.jpg&h=7ba0d6ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://www.nhk.or.jp/dsp/kizuna/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhk.or.jp%2Fdsp%2Fkizuna%2F&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=f646e49a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhk.or.jp/dsp/kizuna/</a><br />\nPV：<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av9037719/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav9037719%2F&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=43545045\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av9037719/</a><br />\n出演：<br />\n役所広司、新垣結衣、岡田將生<br />\n勝地涼、小林薫、田中裕子</div><br />\n  <span style=\"color: red;\">本作品，是東日本大震災受傷的一家，各種困難和戰鬥的同時，地震日出生的小馬夢想的賽馬到成長的身姿，福島縣的相馬舞台壓倒性的描繪的SP電視劇。</span><br />\n  東日本大地震失去了長子的拓馬（岡田將生）的家人，和地震當日出生的小馬相依為命。父親&middot;雅之（役所廣司）和長女&middot;將子（新垣結衣）想將死去的哥哥夢見的競技馬培育起來，母親&middot;佳世子（田中裕子）沉浸在失去了長子的悲痛之中無法自拔。以前是騎手的青年&middot;夏雄（勝地涼）與協助他家人，進行受災地的復興，同時也依靠著作為北海道的牧場主人的加山（小林薰）。於是家庭面臨嚴峻的現實。真的是夢寐以求的競技馬就能夠跑起來嗎？<br />\n廣播：NHK 2017年3月23及24日（前後篇．各73分）<br />\n前篇(字幕)：<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av9351185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav9351185&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=e933bf12\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av9351185</a><br />\n後篇(字幕)：<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av9372173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav9372173&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=eb3eae34\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av9372173</a>"},{"pid":"f8c9c2d75aaad06e07715c360e35ed130b1ec734","tid":182811,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:05:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>新手上路主線攻略：</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/TnYOcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FTnYOcs&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=5bc8f3c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/TnYOcs</a><br />\n歷年LIHKG會員投票參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/WfECpU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FWfECpU&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c8d5cddd\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/WfECpU</a><br />\nB站Gakki綜藝連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/0h1G6W\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F0h1G6W&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=eaff0035\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/0h1G6W</a><br />\nGakki全廣告(Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/Lk8ihS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FLk8ihS&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3bd907d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Lk8ihS</a><br />\n新垣結衣 高清CM 150連發<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av8228403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav8228403&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c31da76e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av8228403</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">日劇冷知識：</span></strong><br />\n日本無分男 / 女主角