nbinc名單：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/Eeyy7O\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FEeyy7O&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=50e9aea0\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Eeyy7O</a><br />\n巴打創作：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/mnrGKF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FmnrGKF&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=83252b8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/mnrGKF</a><br />\n點名&amp;留言版：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/iiJjsq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FiiJjsq&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d84e0823\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/iiJjsq</a>"},{"pid":"a596111a9eef38864a3fa576a01e6148f0e1a7ac","tid":182811,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">新垣結衣x瑛太W主演映畫《ミックス。》(混合雙打)<br />\n挑戰乒乓球題材的浪漫喜劇！ </strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97B91eP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97B91eP.jpg&h=61a86686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TB523R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TB523R.jpg&h=c72bb608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n腳本：古沢良太（Legal High 腳本） <br />\n監督：石川淳一（Legal High 監督） <br />\n<br />\n共演卡司：広末涼子、遠藤憲一、田中美佐子、佐野勇斗、瀬戸康史、永野芽郁、蒼井優、森崎博之、吉田鋼太郎、生瀬勝久、山口紗彌加、斎藤司、久間田琳加、鈴木福、谷花音、真木よう子、小日向文世等。 <br />\n<br />\n 2月中旬開始攝影，2017年秋全國東寶系公開！ 新垣結衣飾演戀愛和工作都很失敗的原天才乒乓球少女、快30歲的單身OL富田多滿子，與瑛太飾演的原日本職業拳擊手組合成乒乓球混雙，向全國大賽挑戰的故事。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>《Code Blue 3》製作決定!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/100302_53bdee902bf86890010775dc3176e6ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F100302_53bdee902bf86890010775dc3176e6ed.jpg&h=039dc2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5月開拍，時間設定於第2季的七年後，播放時間：7月份 月九<br />\n十年過去，各人都走上自己的人生道路。<br />\n藍沢耕作（山下智久）離開咗翔陽大學附屬醫院嘅急症室之後，喺腦外科深造研究，目標係成為最強嘅腦外科醫生。<br />\n白石恵（新垣結衣）就繼續喺人手不足嘅翔北急症室工作，成為咗飛行救護團隊嘅領導醫生奮鬥中！<br />\n緋山美帆子（戸田恵梨香）就去咗備產醫療中心，喺婦產科果度深造。<br />\n冴島はるか（比嘉愛未）依家繼續做緊飛行團隊嘅護士。<br />\n藤川一男（浅利洋介）同白石一齊留咗喺翔北急症室，只係自己向着成為整形外科嘅急症室醫生之路進發。<br />\n面臨新挑戰，失去家人，開始戀愛，在新嘅階段有邊個對手等緊佢哋？<br />\n來自 Gakki 的訊息：<br />\n  「在最初的《Code Blue》拍攝中收到的20歲生日祝福，好像已經過了很久，又像是最近的事。在這20代的最後一年再次扮演白石惠，以及劇組時隔7年的集結，感受到極大的緣分和使命感。全新的《Code Blue》故事中，狀況、立場、所有的事物都有很大的改變，當時一起努力著的5人會有什麼發展我非常期待。希望能讓觀眾看得開心，也希望能夠有所收穫，我會全力以赴的！」<br />\n<a href=\"http://ricgrady.pixnet.net/blog/post/117081740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fricgrady.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F117081740&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=fd7621ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://ricgrady.pixnet.net/blog/post/117081740</a>"},{"pid":"b964d9aeaf57f0510ba8b40b89f418704cc55d5a","tid":182811,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9103c79e74cbbb10f68ce4e3327a4c31efbf3949","tid":182811,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b2bd1a673e37e4c2365bc8952d58b00ccad817","tid":182811,"uid":5808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:07:42.000Z","msg":"留埋名先"},{"pid":"7d847f40318a84ba0f668e87a757e915b49be459","tid":182811,"uid":37890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:08:12.000Z","msg":"唔理,留左先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5089c8b3942e5faf3bf025fd38482d18dce21a98","tid":182811,"uid":14119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"????"},{"pid":"149c00d79b20db0a71d565572b7189aaa62e7b10","tid":182811,"uid":82436,"like":0